summary: Wooloo is the cutest thing ever, craving stability, disliking conflicts and simply rolling away from its problems? so wholesome!...
caption:
Wooloo is the cutest thing ever, craving stability, disliking conflicts and simply rolling away from its problems? so wholesome! so adorable! spirit animal material!!
…all the while sporting badass Viking braids.

A solemn salute to innocent people traumatized by less innocent people rule34ing Wooloo; I raise you, perverting it in different ways.Yup, I added a historically-inaccurate horned Viking helmet to go with the braids. A battleaxe because… reasons? Getting rid of your problems by rolling on them. And. Uh. Apparently Age of Empires ate my brain or something.
